data.description: SPACIOUS NW HOME W/ TWO MASTER SUITES! SPACIOUS NW HOME W/ TWO MASTER SUITES! 4 brm 4 ba home! Located in a very desirable neighborhood. Grand layout with plenty of room everywhere. Living room with gas fireplace blends into an arched doorway to dining area. Kitchen hosts tile counters, tons of cabinets, a pantry, gas oven, full appliances, and stainless refrigerator. Breakfast nook area with slider glass doors leads to the interior laundry. Family room hosts a wet bar area and a barndoor bathroom with upgraded handicap walk-in shower. Extended enclosed patio features a brand new jacuzzi! Upstairs has four bedrooms, two of which are fitted with their own private bathrooms. One of the bedrooms has sliding doors opening out to a wide tiled floor roof patio. Entertain friends and family under the beautiful starlit nights!! Full length patio also out back with a brand new Tuff Shed. Wide  RV parking driveway or park inside the iron gates. Deep 2-car garage. Cooled by two evap coolers. Cool water feature out front adds to the ambiance. Leased PPA solar agreement is $245/mo. FOR THOSE SEEKING SPACE AND COMFORT INSIDE & OUT!
